string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Solo_Israphel_03
string.body: Trust me when I say you'll thank me later....

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tiamat_Voice1
string.body: You've killed Sharbokan, but it will be your final victory.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tiamat_Voice2
string.body: Insolent Daevas! Destroying my lieutenants!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tiamat_Voice3
string.body: Laksyaka was useful to me. You'll see what happens to those who take away my tools.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tiamat_Voice4
string.body: Whatever agony my lieutenants felt as they died, you will feel tenfold!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kalyndi_Spawn_1
string.body: Dear Dragon Lord, please rest in peace. Let me avenge you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kaisinel_T_01
string.body: We're in time!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kaisinel_T_02
string.body: You should be honored, Tiamat. I came in person to kill you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kaisinel_T_03
string.body: It is my destiny to destroy you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kaisinel_T_04
string.body: I am weakening. You Daevas must take your turn.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Marchutan_T_01
string.body: We're not too late!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Marchutan_T_02
string.body: It's been a while, Tiamat.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Marchutan_T_03
string.body: If that's what destiny asks of me, I'll accept it.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Marchutan_T_04
string.body: I must rest a moment. Hold off the Dragon while I do!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_NPC_Tiamat_2_01
string.body: You, you must be...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_NPC_Tiamat_2_02
string.body: You will face not only my wrath but Fregion's as well!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_NPC_Tiamat_2_03
string.body: Behold the true power of a Dragon Lord!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kaisinel_T_05
string.body: Dragon Lord! Be silent and accept your fate!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kaisinel_T_06
string.body: It is finally over.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kaisinel_T_07
string.body: Even a Dragon Lord can be driven to madness.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Marchutan_T_05
string.body: Silence! There's nothing you can do to save yourself.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Marchutan_T_06
string.body: Finally, Tiamat is dead.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Marchutan_T_07
string.body: I saw its despair, before the end.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tiamat_T_01
string.body: Aaarrgghhh!!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Guardian_EnterAttackState
string.body: Thou shalt never leave this room!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Guardian_OnDie
string.body: My Lord...Forgive me...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Chantra_EnterAttackState
string.body: There is nowhere to run. Nowere to hide!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Chantra_OnDie
string.body: Tell Tiamat... I died fighting for our cause.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Sadha_EnterAttackState
string.body: Don't I remember you troublemakers from the Dredgion?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Sadha_OnDie
string.body: How humiliating... to die at your hand.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kumbanda_EntterAttackState
string.body: Let's get this over with. I have things to do.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kumbanda_OnDie
string.body: I regret nothing in my life, not even treachery.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Rakshaka_EnterAttackState
string.body: I devote myself to the Dragon Lord!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Rakshaka_OnDie
string.body: Argh...!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Anuhart_EnterAttackState01
string.body: So many familiar faces, I see. Well, today wilt be thy final day!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Anuhart_EnterAttackState02
string.body: Consider it an honor to die by my hand.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Anuhart_UseSkill
string.body: I will crush you all!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Anuhart_OnDie
string.body: Tahabata, please avenge me... Eurrrrgh!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tahabata_EnterAttackState
string.body: I've been keeping my flames warm for you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tahabata_OnDie
string.body: How... dare you...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kalyndi_WakeUp
string.body: Thinkest thou to defeat the Dragon Lord? First thou must survive my flames!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Kalyndi_OnDie
string.body: I may die, but my flames live on!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tiamat_GuardianDie
string.body: You've killed Sharbokan, but it will be your final victory.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tiamat_SadhaDie
string.body: Insolent Daevas! Destroying my lieutenants!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tiamat_RakshakaDie
string.body: Laksyaka was useful to me. You'll see what happens to those who take away my tools.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tiamat_TahabataDie
string.body: Whatever agony my lieutenants felt as they died, you will feel tenfold!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tiamat_SummonKalyndi
string.body: Calindi! Show them what true agony is!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_Tiamat_KalyndiDie
string.body: Calindi, your death is not in vain.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_TiamatDragon1_EnterAttackState
string.body: I am the god of death, come to bring your doom!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_TiamatDragon1_UseSkill
string.body: Siel's Relics will ensure our victory!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_TiamatDragon1_OnDie
string.body: What? It was not supposed to be this way!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_TiamatDragon2_WakeUp
string.body: You think you've weakened me? Hah!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_TiamatDragon2_UseSkill01
string.body: Every crisis feeds me strength!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_TiamatDragon2_UseSkill02
string.body: That's it! I'm out of patience!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_TiamatDragon2_UseSkill03
string.body: I'll finish you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_TiamatDragon2_UseSkill04
string.body: You'll wish you'd stayed in your beds today.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_TiamatDragon2_OnDie
string.body: I... am... immortal...!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLDF5Re_02_Priest_FireD_Gossip1
string.body: It's burning out of control. I need something to fight back the flames!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLDF5Re_02_Priest_EleD_Gossip1
string.body: This electricity is powerful. I need something to absorb it.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLDF5Re_02_Priest_PoisonD_Gossip1
string.body: The poison is eating away at me... Heal me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_UserCheck_01_Gossip
string.body: It's been quite a while since someone tried to steal the fruits of my research... Could be interesting. I'll give you 15 minutes. Go!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_UserAllKill_01_Gossip
string.body: My only son is safe at last.... My son? Where is he?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_Enter_02_Gossip
string.body: Be gone!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_Enter_03_Gossip
string.body: You will not hinder my craft!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_Enter_04_Gossip
string.body: Awake, my children!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_Enter_05_Gossip
string.body: I have no wish to fight, but I will protect my child!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_ImitaionSay_01_Gossip
string.body: Which one, which one...

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_ImitaionSay_02_Gossip
string.body: Let's see how you handle this!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_ImitaionSay_03_Gossip
string.body: Death is not the end.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_ImitaionSay_04_Gossip
string.body: You cannot evade my power!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_ImitaionSay_05_Gossip
string.body: As soon as I gather my energy, your fate will be sealed.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_ImitaionSay_06_Gossip
string.body: Death shall place its icy hand on your shoulder, and then, darkness!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_SpawnOrder_01_Gossip
string.body: Rise, my children, rise!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_Enter_05_2_Gossip
string.body: It ends now.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Rune_Die_Gossip
string.body: My son… I see him before me… I am coming!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Boss_01
string.body: Attack! Destroy the gate for Beritra!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Boss_02
string.body: Take this!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Boss_03
string.body: You, the commander? My foot, haha!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Boss_04
string.body: Think again, small fry. You're no match to me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Boss_05
string.body: You are stronger than I expected, but I'm through playing around!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Boss_06
string.body: Resistence is futile.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Boss_07
string.body: Defeated, you say? Who are you kidding?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Boss_Katk2_b
string.body: Victory is mine!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Boss_Kcast6_b
string.body: You all!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Boss_Katk6_b
string.body: Away, into the darkness!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Commander_Li_01
string.body: In the name of Empyrean Lord Kaisinel! Daevas! Defend your posts!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Commander_Li_02
string.body: The enemy commander, here to fight me directly? What a fool!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Commander_Li_03
string.body: Is that all you've got? You must be joking!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Commander_Li_04
string.body: Steady! As soon as we dispatch this one, victory and glory are ours!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Commander_Da_01
string.body: In the name of Empyrean Lord Marchutan! Daevas! Defend your posts!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Commander_Da_02
string.body: The enemy commander, here to fight me directly? What a fool!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Commander_Da_03
string.body: Is that all you've got? You must be joking!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_Commander_Da_04
string.body: Steady! As soon as we dispatch this one, victory and glory are ours!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF5_TD_DragonRider_01
string.body: Let's ride!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss1_01
string.body: With this power I might even become the Fifth Dragon Lord!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss1_02
string.body: Let me show you what you get for sticking your nose in where it isn't wanted!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss1_03
string.body: You too will be like these children.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss1_04
string.body: Every part of your being will scream for mercy.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss1_05
string.body: Your reward for your efforts... will be to hear the screams of the Danuar!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss1_06
string.body: our screams of terror will resound across the pillars! As did the Danuar...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss1_07
string.body: Bwahaha! I am the Dragon Lord! The Dragon Lord!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss1_kcast5_b
string.body: Can you feel the terror inside you? Down to your very bones?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss1_kcast7_b
string.body: The spiteful shrills... They are music to my ears.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss1_katk7_b
string.body: Hear that?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss2_01
string.body: As Lady Sheba wills me…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss2_02
string.body: Weaklings! I shall slay you all!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss2_03
string.body: Thy attacks are as nothing to me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss2_04
string.body: I am Ahuradim, Defender of the Bastion!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss2_05
string.body: Thy persistence is notable… I shall redouble my efforts!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss2_06
string.body: I… shall not… fall!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss2_07
string.body: My protection of this base is complete upon thy death.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss2_08
string.body: Achradim Gossip Temp

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss3_01
string.body: Danuar trash... But they have learned!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss3_02
string.body: Thy secrets spill out under my interrogation.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss3_Katk6_b
string.body: Fear not, pain is not your concern.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss3_Katk7_b
string.body: Fear not, your life ends soon.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss3_Kcast5_b
string.body: Who… who are you? Who... Who am I?!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss3_Katk5_b
string.body: Thy knowledge of pain is rudimentary. I teach thee.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss4_01
string.body: Thy soul, Daeva, possesseth no strength.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss4_02
string.body: Our pens run empty. Daevas arrive in time to fill them.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss4_03
string.body: Move, guards! Protect me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss4_04
string.body: Power be not in the limbs of puny Daevas.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss4_05
string.body: Mine honor is tarnished, but thy death restores me.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss4_06
string.body: It is over.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss5_01
string.body: Uterunerk takes all shiny ancient things, akakak.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss5_02
string.body: Out of Uterunerk's way! No profit sharing allowed.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss5_03
string.body: Leave Shugo be! Nyerk!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss5_04
string.body: Please forget this! Shugo pays well!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss5_05
string.body: This... This will stop it... Nyerk!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDVritra_Base_Boss5_06
string.body: Uterunerk still has luck, akakak. No dying today.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_Post_1st_Start_Gossip
string.body: Confusion now hath made his masterpiece! A Daeva challenges me.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_Post_1st_End_Gossip
string.body: For Beritra's glory.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_Post_1st_Skill_Gossip
string.body: Death's sweet embrace enfolds you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_Post_2nd_Start_Gossip
string.body: You are a tedius fool.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_Post_2nd_End_Gossip
string.body: Thou common Qooqoo...

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_Post_2nd_Skill_Gossip
string.body: Hah! Perish on my blade!

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_Post_3rd_Start_Gossip
string.body: What worm is this?

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_Post_3rd_End_Gossip
string.body: You ply your trade... with skill.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_Post_3rd_Skill_Gossip
string.body: Hast thou a love of death?

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_1stBoss_Start_Gossip
string.body: Thou hast courage, but lack in sense.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_1stBoss_End_Gossip
string.body: Beritra's glory reigns forever.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_1stBoss_Skill_Gossip
string.body: Come! Let me unhair thy head.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Vri_1stBoss_Skill2_Gossip
string.body: Cower before me, wretched worm.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Shulack_Keeper_01_Batk
string.body: What? What do you want?

string.body: The boss doesn't like it when I waste company time. Scram!

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Shulack_Keeper_03_Katk_b
string.body: Bow before me. I command it!

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Shulack_Keeper_04_Broad
string.body: No, no. Oh, no. Please, leave me alone.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Shulack_Keeper_05_Gossip
string.body: Stop trying to distract me.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Ratman_01_Katk1_b
string.body: MuMu! Help me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Ratman_02_Broad
string.body: MuMu MuMu!

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Ratman_03_Gossip
string.body: Shugo sent bestiful MuMu home. All my work was done. Mu!

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Ratman_04_Katk2_b
string.body: MuMu...?

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Ratman_05_Idle_b
string.body: I wanna go home.

string.body: Kobold dying. Make help?

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Brownie_02_Broad
string.body: Wing take mercy Kobold. No hitting.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Brownie_03_Gossip
string.body: Kobold good. Kobold gentle!

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Brownie_04_Katk2_b
string.body: Kobold wish. Wish home. Wish food.

string.name: STR_CHAT_BLDF5_Brownie_05_Idle_b
string.body: Kobold misses home.

string.body: Come around behind them!

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_As_Broad_02
string.body: The enemy is here!

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_As_Broad_03
string.body: You think you can boss me around?

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_As_Broad_04
string.body: You'll die alone and scared.

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Lizard_Broad_01
string.body: Surround them!

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Lizard_Broad_02
string.body: Destroy the enemy!

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Lizard_Broad_03
string.body: I make my own orders.

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Lizard_Broad_04
string.body: I follow my own way.l

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_1_Batk_b
string.body: There's no way a simple Daeva can challenge me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_2_Batk_b
string.body: You're such an absent-minded fool.

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Lizard_1_Batk_b
string.body: Live and let... Forget it. Just die!

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Lizard_2_Batk_b
string.body: I won't go down so easily.

string.body: Tiamat... I go to meet you now...

string.body: This is the end? How... disappointing.

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Lizard_1_Die_b
string.body: It can't be...

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Lizard_2_Die_b
string.body: I was to kill you, but now I perish at your hands?

string.body: How could a puny Daeva challenge my might?

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_SemiNamed_2_Batk_b
string.body: The Tiamat Legion will grind your bones to ashes beneath their feet!

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_SemiNamed_1_Die_b
string.body: But you're only a Daeva! How did this happen...

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_SemiNamed_2_Die_b
string.body: No! It can't end like this.

string.body: Beritra... Beritra...

string.name: STR_CHAT_TR_Drakan_BrainWashing_1_Die_b
string.body: Beritra...? Tiamat...

string.name: STR_CHAT_LDF5b_Ratman_Sleep_02

string.body: Qooqoo! Qooqoo!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDRose_M_ShugoM_Wi_S_N_2_Katk2_b

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDDF3_T_Boss_Gossip_01
string.body: Beritra is truly unstoppable!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDSeal_Q_Boss_Teleport_01
string.body: If you're ready, I will take you to Agony's Well.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLF1_Vanq_Comad_Gossip_01
string.body: This isn't nearly enough…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLF1_Vanq_Comad_Gossip_02
string.body: I need a stronger Balaur!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLF1_Vanq_Comad_Gossip_03
string.body: Now, at last... you're mine.

string.name: STR_CHAT_event_toy_bear_Gossip
string.body: Hey, you! Come here and press the button on my belly!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Shugo_AB1_30_Gossip_01
string.body: The Draconic Design Merchant went below, daeva.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Shugo_AB1_30_Gossip_02
string.body: The daeva deserves nice things. Find Draconic Designs on the lower level.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Shugo_AB1_30_Gossip_03
string.body: Go! The Draconic merchants and other Shugos are downstairs!

string.name: STR_CHAT_event_toy_01_Gossip
string.body: Hairung...

string.name: STR_CHAT_event_toy_02_Gossip
string.body: Hairing...

string.name: STR_CHAT_event_toy_03_Gossip
string.body: Give me your bonus cards or I'll eat you alive!

string.name: STR_CHAT_event_lucky_01_Gossip
string.body: I've gotta get away quickly, nyerk! Let's make some deals before I go!

string.name: STR_CHAT_event_lucky_02_Gossip
string.body: I don't have much time left, nyerk! I'll be gone soon, nyerk!

string.name: STR_CHAT_event_lucky_03_Gossip
string.body: Candies… Candies… I could use them now!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_G1_Event_DFBoss_Gossip_01
string.body: Enemies incoming! Annihilate them!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_G2_Event_Boss_Gossip_01
string.body: Scouting complete! Board the ship immediately!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LDF3_GrandRVR_DefBoss_01
string.body: I'll take the Balaur down no matter what!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LDF3_GrandRVR_AtkBoss_01
string.body: Victory is ours! Onto the next strike!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LDF3_GrandRVR_DefBoss_02
string.body: That didn't work out. Retreat!

string.name: STR_CHAT_LDF3_GrandRVR_AtkBoss_02
string.body: We're getting overwhelmed. Retreat!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Officer_01
string.body: It seems like Atreia is full of weird weather these days. Earthquakes, typhoons… Be careful out there!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Officer_02
string.body: I hear the Library of the Sage of Sanctum just got new books! Expanding the mind is as vital as improving the body, you know. You should go!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Officer_03
string.body: Strange cracks have been showing up all across Atreia. No one knows what's going on yet, so take caution out there! Return to the Sanctum as much as possible!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Officer_04
string.body: Elyos is becoming less and less of a safe haven as the Asmodians turn up their ferocity with us. The Sanctum will not tolerate it! We will respond without mercy!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Officer_05
string.body: Some rebellious propoganda has been going around. Don't believe everything you read. And destroy any if you find it.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Officer_06
string.body: Lord Ariel's Agent is about to recruit some elite legion members. I hope they get plenty of capable Daevas as applicants!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Officer_07
string.body: 'Our King is Still a Slumber There' is a book interpreting the history of Aion with a new perspective. It's been labeled as rebellious material though, due to false and seditious content. I wouldn't be caught carrying it around if I were you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Conversation_01
string.body: And I... will always love you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Conversation_02
string.body: Ugh, that song is ancient!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Conversation_03
string.body: Look, kid. You're not old enough to appreciate all the sorrowful nuance of this song, all right?

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Conversation_04
string.body: Another song! Another song!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Conversation_05
string.body: Hmm. What about the Ballad of the Lost Hero? Sound interesting?

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Conversation_06
string.body: Wow! Yeah, I like it!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Conversation_07
string.body: I'll sing that one, then. Long ago, Aion chose a great hero, whose name was…

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Conversation_08
string.body: Yawn! What a boring opening!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Conversation_09
string.body: I see.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Prophet_01
string.body: Soon enough, fate will wash over you like one great wave. It can neither be avoided nor defeated--all you can do is face your destiny with your chin held high.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Prophet_02
string.body: I see an ominous star looming over you, casting a great shadow. Your decisions will determine if you destroy the star, or if it destroys you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Prophet_03
string.body: When gazing in the mirror early in the morning, don't become too captivated by yourself. You may overlook what else is lurking there...

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Prophet_04
string.body: No matter where you step now, you are surrounded by crossroads. Don't get lost in the labyrinth.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Prophet_05
string.body: Atreia stands on the brink of change. The course of history will never be the same. Trust nothing. The truth will ever be lurking behind you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Prophet_06
string.body: Past and future are fated to meet soon enough, throwing the world into chaos. Keep your eyes on the present.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_LC1_Prophet_07
string.body: Time will move soon enough, shaking the whole of the world. But do not worry, Daeva. Your wings will stretch to freedoms you have never known before.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Officer_01
string.body: It seems like Atreia is full of weird weather these days. Earthquakes, typhoons… Be careful out there!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Officer_02
string.body: New books have arrived in the Temple of Knowledge in Pandaemonium! Training your mind is just as important as training your body!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Officer_03
string.body: Mysterious cracks and noises have been reported all across Atreia. I'd recommend staying in Pandaemonium until we figure out what's causing it.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Officer_04
string.body: Asmodae is becoming less and less of a safe haven as the Elyos continue to attack us. Pandaemonium will not tolerate it! We will respond without mercy!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Officer_05
string.body: Some rebellious propoganda has been going around. Don't believe everything you read.... and destroy any, if you find it.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Officer_06
string.body: Lord Azphel's Agent is about to recruit some elite legion members. I hope a lot of capable Daevas apply!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Officer_07
string.body: 'Our King is Still a Slumber There' is a book interpreting the history of Aion with a new perspective. It's been labeled as rebellious material though, due to false and seditious content. I wouldn't be caught carrying it around, if I were you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Conversation_01
string.body: Country roads, take me home....

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Conversation_02
string.body: Isn't that song a little old? Sing something else!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Conversation_03
string.body: It may be old, but it's a classic for a reason. It's about...

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Conversation_04
string.body: Another song! Another song!

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Conversation_05
string.body: All right, fine. What about the Ballad of the Forgotten Hero? Would you like that?

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Conversation_06
string.body: Let's hear it.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Conversation_07
string.body: There once was a hero of fate.... Chosen by Aion to be great...

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Conversation_08
string.body: No. Please stop.

string.name: STR_CHAT_HighDeva_DC1_Conversation_09
string.body: Sorry...

string.body: You look better....

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_01_OPEN
string.body: The gate is open. The time has come!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_HighDeva_M_01
string.body: Your memories will return with this battle. Ready yourself!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_HighDeva_M_02
string.body: Behold the might of Earth!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_HighDeva_M_03
string.body: Waves of Destiny take you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_HighDeva_M_04
string.body: Be engulfed by the Storm of Wrath!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_HighDeva_F_01
string.body: Your memories will return with this battle. Ready yourself!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_HighDeva_F_02
string.body: Behold the might of Earth!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_HighDeva_F_03
string.body: Waves of Destiny take you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_HighDeva_F_04
string.body: Be engulfed by the Storm of Wrath!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_01
string.body: The Balaur are here!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_02
string.body: No one leaves here alive!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_03
string.body: Keep fighting! Reinforcements are on the way!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_04
string.body: Shards! Where did they come from?

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_05
string.body: Kill the intruders!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_06
string.body: Where are our reinforcements?

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_07
string.body: The Indratu Legion is attacking!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_08
string.body: Die, you cowards!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_09
string.body: New Heiron needs reinforcements! Now!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_10
string.body: The Balaur are here!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_11
string.body: Kill them all!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_12
string.body: Reinforcements are coming!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_13
string.body: Shards! Where did they come from?

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_14
string.body: Kill them! Now!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_15
string.body: Where are our reinforcements?

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_16
string.body: The Bakarma Legion has us surrounded!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_17
string.body: Die, you blasted cowards!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_18
string.body: Beluslan shall fall without reinforcements!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_19
string.body: Kneel before the Indratu Legion!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_20
string.body: Charge!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_21
string.body: Leave none behind! Spill their blood!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_22
string.body: I shall show you the might of Indratu!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_23
string.body: I shall trample you into dust!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_24
string.body: Haha!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_25
string.body: Resist and die, you fools!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_26
string.body: Not bad...

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_27
string.body: You'll never escape!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_28
string.body: For Victory! For Bakarma!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_29
string.body: Attack!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_30
string.body: Take them out! All of them!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_31
string.body: Hold nothing back!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_32
string.body: You will all die here!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_33
string.body: Haha!

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_34
string.body: Your time is up.

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_35
string.body: Impressive...

string.name: STR_RVR_Guard_direction_36
string.body: There's no escape!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Leibo_01
string.body: Guards! An unwelcome Daeva!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Leibo_02
string.body: Intruder!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Leibo_03
string.body: Here, already?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Leibo_04
string.body: Stop following me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Leibo_05
string.body: I didn't complete the seal, unfortunately.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Sado_Fi_N_01_01
string.body: You will not pass!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Sado_Fi_N_02_01
string.body: You dare intrude?!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Sado_Fi_N_02_02
string.body: We are not defeated!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Sado_Fi_N_03_01
string.body: Begone!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Sado_Fi_N_03_02
string.body: Protect the Library!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Sado_Pr_N_01_01
string.body: Leave these sacred grounds!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Sado_Pr_N_02_01
string.body: You are not welcome!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Sado_Pr_N_02_02
string.body: This is not the end!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Sado_Pr_N_03_01
string.body: This ends now!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Sado_Pr_N_03_02
string.body: We will protect these halls!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Leibo_06
string.body: Guards! Apprehend the intruder!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Leibo_07
string.body: Guards, take the intruder!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_Q_Leibo_08
string.body: Leave me alone!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Free_Guard_Gossip_01
string.body: Thank you for saving me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Free_Guard_Gossip_02
string.body: And I thought all was lost.

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Free_Guard_Gossip_03
string.body: Am I still alive?

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Event_G1_Da_Boss_Spawn_Gossip_01
string.body: Wretches!! Your resistance shall be futile.

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Event_G1_Da_Boss_Spawn_Gossip_02
string.body: Let's show these cowardly Elyos the might of the Asmodians!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Event_G1_Da_Boss_Spawn_Gossip_03
string.body: Don't give up! The will of Empyrean Lord Azphel is with us.

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Event_G1_Li_Boss_Spawn_Gossip_01
string.body: Victory is a certainty for us Elyos, yet you continue your futile struggles.

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Event_G1_Li_Boss_Spawn_Gossip_02
string.body: You're no fools. Haven't you yet realized that this isn't a battle you can win?

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Event_G1_Li_Boss_Spawn_Gossip_03
string.body: Are there really this many Asmodians ignorant of their fate…? Then I'll teach you here and now. That today is your last day alive!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Event_G1_Da_Boss_Change_Gossip_01
string.body: Empyrean Lord Azphel! Please give me strength.

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Event_G1_Li_Boss_Change_Gossip_01
string.body: Lord Ariel! Please show your power to that Asmodian!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLUNA_SIEGE_Soldier_Q_01_GOSSIP_01
string.body: Hey!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLUNA_SIEGE_Soldier_Kn_N_An_01_GOSSIP_01
string.body: For the peace of Atreia!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLUNA_SIEGE_NPC_GOSSIP_03
string.body: Shulack am ready for battle.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLUNA_SIEGE_S1_Shulack_Fi_An_01_Gossip_01
string.body: Shulack destroy you all!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLUNA_SIEGE_S1_Shulack_Gu_An_01_Gossip_01
string.body: Fire! Fire! Fire!

string.name: STR_CHAT_event_ppobarung_01_Gossip
string.body: Take a look at my new invention...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF6_LF1_Help_GOSSIP_01
string.body: The Thorn Tentacle Traps in the Supply Box are critical for this mission.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF6_LF1_Help_GOSSIP_02
string.body: Those who have the Thorn Tentacle Traps follows me! Everyone else go destroy the iron fence!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF6_LF1_Help_GOSSIP_03
string.body: Everyone else should catch a monitoring device and exit to the left.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF6_LF1_Help_GOSSIP_04
string.body: Set up a Thorn Tentacle Trap here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF6_LF1_Help_GOSSIP_05
string.body: I will go and stop Lieutenant Anuhart. Please catch up with your group.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF6_LF1_Help_GOSSIP_06
string.body: Is it really impossible to kill Lieutenant Anuhart...?

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Free_Dejabobo_Gossip_01
string.body: What's taking you so long? There's a large piece of Aether just around the corner. Go secure it!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Free_Dejabobo_Gossip_02
string.body: I thought I was a goner. The pure Aether piece is near the Tarha Krall village. Go secure the piece, I'll be okay...

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Free_Dejabobo_Gossip_03
string.body: My strength wanes... I must make it back to shelter and rest. Go on ahead... we'll meet again, Daeva!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Free_Wizabobo_Gossip_01
string.body: Up ahead lies an Aether piece, Daeva. You must hurry and secure it!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Free_Wizabobo_Gossip_02
string.body: This will not end well for us! Go find the Aether piece in the Zenzen Village.

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Free_Wizabobo_Gossip_03
string.body: I've become too weak, Daeva... I must find shelter... Fight bravely...

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Guardian_Gossip_01
string.body: You've secured a fragment of the Tower of Eternity! We will recover it for you, keep fighting!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Guardian_Gossip_02
string.body: Those wounds look serious. Take care, Daeva, and continue the fight.

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Guardian_Gossip_03
string.body: Well done, Deva. Return to Ariel's Tempere Shrine and report to the agent there.

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Archon_Gossip_01
string.body: That's a piece of the Tower of Eternity! Keep fighting and we'll take care of this piece for you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Archon_Gossip_02
string.body: Get back to the fight… we'll take care of this!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F6_Archon_Gossip_03
string.body: That was well fought, Deva! Return to Azraphel's Tempere Shrine and report to the agent there.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDF6_LF1_Alarm_GOSSIP_01
string.body: Intruder detected! Activating Speed Mode upon Anuhart's arrival!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Nepilim_Sun_GOSSIP_01
string.body: All attack! Protect our Lord!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Tower_Nmd_01
string.body: Intruder detected!!!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Nepilim_Nmd_01
string.body: You'll never leave here alive!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Nepilim_Nmd_02
string.body: Attack!!!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Nepilim_Nmd_03
string.body: Witness the power of a true warrior!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Nepilim_Nmd_04
string.body: Fire! Fire! Aim for their heads!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Nepilim_Nmd_05
string.body: Ungh… I am hit….

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Snake_Nmd_01
string.body: Let none escape their fate!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Snake_Nmd_02
string.body: Your skills are impressive, but they won't be enough to defeat me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Snake_Nmd_03
string.body: There is no mercy for you, only the end of my blade!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Snake_Nmd_04
string.body: Surely now this is proof of the prophecy….

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Nepilim_01
string.body: It might already be too late….

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Nepilim_02
string.body: I will end you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Nepilim_03
string.body: My sword is the last thing you will ever see.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLDF5_Under_02_War_Shugo_Fix_Gossip
string.body: I'm a salesman, not a fighter!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLDF5_Under_02_War_Shugo_Worker_Gossip
string.body: Hang in there! Nyerk!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLDF5_Under_02_War_Ratman_Sleep
string.body: Zzzzzzz...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDLDF5_Under_02_War_Brownie_Worker_Gossip
string.body: Everywhere I look there's something to do. Back to work!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_polymorph_end_GOSSIP_01
string.body: Thanks to you I was able to wake up!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_polymorph_end_GOSSIP_02
string.body: I can open the path to the Contaminated Library, but I'm not strong enough to join you in your fight.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Nepilim_Key_GOSSIP_01
string.body: If you want to pass, you must defeat me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Tower_Key_GOSSIP_01
string.body: The doors to the Vile Library has been locked! Destroy the locking mechanism to open the door to the Cliff of Destruction.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Event_Guard_GOSSIP_01
string.body: I'll return to the advance party. Watch your back; with the barrier gone no one is safe.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Nepilim_Earth_GOSSIP_01
string.body: I'll never surrender.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Nepilim_Earth_GOSSIP_02
string.body: You appear to be laboring under a false sense of hope. Pitifull…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_D_Guard_GOSSIP_01

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Normal_Gossip_04
string.body: Kill the intruders!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Gossip_01
string.body: My queen of the cold Abyss, open your eyes!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Gossip_02
string.body: You can't keep us from resurrecting her!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Gossip_03
string.body: You're not getting any further!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Gossip_04
string.body: Ugh...…Stop...…Stop it!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Gossip_05
string.body: Ahhhhhhh!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Gossip_06
string.body: Father...… Forgive me...…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Gossip_07
string.body: Aughhhhh!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Gossip_08
string.body: Taste cold fury!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Gossip_09
string.body: Bow, peasant! You witness the queen's power!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Gossip_10
string.body: Let me hear your screams!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Gossip_11
string.body: My queen, grant me your protection!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Gossip_12
string.body: May the queen have mercy on you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Witch_Gossip_01
string.body: Oh great queen, open your eyes so we may bask in your glory!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Hero_Gossip_01
string.body: We have to clear those roots to move on. I'm on it!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Hero_Gossip_02
string.body: My strength… is fading. We still need to clear those roots! Help me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Hero_Gossip_03
string.body: Stand back, I'll handle this.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Hero_Gossip_04
string.body: There's no end to them… Keep going, I'll handle this!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Witch_Gossip_02
string.body: You will go no further, Daeva!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Smigol_Gossip_01
string.body: That's not yours…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Smigol_Gossip_02
string.body: Give me back my treasure!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Smigol_Gossip_03
string.body: Something as puny as you? Wants MY treasure?!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Smigol_Gossip_04
string.body: My… treasure...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Leader_Gossip_01
string.body: I will show you the path to eternal peace.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Leader_Gossip_02
string.body: I will grant you your final rest.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Leader_Gossip_03
string.body: Wake up!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Sub_Gossip_01
string.body: Please, help me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Sub_Gossip_02
string.body: Ugh, you must be purified!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Sub_Gossip_05
string.body: My son...… Please avenge him...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Sub_Gossip_06
string.body: Hrk…. Is he safe…?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Sub_Gossip_07
string.body: I will deliver your souls to the warden!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_01
string.body: Intruders!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_02
string.body: Kill the intruders!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_03
string.body: So this is where they kept you. Stand back, I'll break down the door!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_04
string.body: Follow the passage at the Path of Serenity. Make sure you don't hurt your wings.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_05
string.body: Be careful, the Harvesters are guarding the Path of Serenity!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_06
string.body: Now please, rescue the imprisoned Daevas!! Hurry!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_07
string.body: Are you here to help? The Balaur have the key!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_08
string.body: Thank you… please, you have to help the others!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_09
string.body: Whew, I thought I was done for. Thank you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_10
string.body: Thank you… I thought I was going to die here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_11
string.body: I was so scared… Thank you for rescuing me…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_12
string.body: A Daeva rescue is about the last thing I expected. Thank you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_13
string.body: The Harvesters are here! Ah… Help!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_14
string.body: You saved my life. Once again, I'm in your debt.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_15
string.body: Stop the intruders!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_War_Gossip_01
string.body: The battle at Evergale Canyon rages on.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_War_Gossip_02
string.body: Our job is to retrieve the core fragments.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_War_Gossip_03
string.body: Make sure we win!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_War_Gossip_04
string.body: Can you help me?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_War_Gossip_05
string.body: My strength is returning.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_War_Gossip_06
string.body: There's still a fragment in the cave.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_War_Gossip_07
string.body: I'm getting weaker….

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_War_Gossip_08
string.body: I need the Dew of Life.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_16
string.body: Urgh, I can't… move…!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_17
string.body: This place is a nightmare.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_18
string.body: Please, let me out…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_19
string.body: Agh… ow….

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_20
string.body: I just want to go home…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_21
string.body: Rebellious Daevas were taken to the Rehabilitation Jail in the sky.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_22
string.body: Use the jail pulley and you'll be able to rescue them.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_23
string.body: Thank you for releasing the prisoners.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_24
string.body: An intruder!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_25
string.body: Get them!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_26
string.body: They're escaping!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_27
string.body: Get them!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_28
string.body: Where did they come from?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_29
string.body: You're in my way!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_30
string.body: How did they get out?!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_31
string.body: For the queen!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_32
string.body: How dare you come here!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_33
string.body: Guard the generator!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_34
string.body: You destroyed the holy Sakra!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_35
string.body: Struggle all you want, the Incarna will still devour you!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_03_Gosship_30
string.body: Now!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_03_Gosship_31
string.body: The Artifact Core will be in our care now.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_03_Gosship_32
string.body: I'm at my wit's end...…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_03_Gosship_33
string.body: Now!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_03_Gosship_34
string.body: The Artifact Core will be in our care now.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_03_Gosship_35
string.body: This is the best I can do…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_36
string.body: There's nowhere to go!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_37
string.body: My jewel is gone!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_38
string.body: You have to find my jewel and bring it back to me. Don't keep it!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_39
string.body: Did you find my jewel? Give it back!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_Final_Boss_Hero_Gossip_01
string.body: I will destroy the ice cluster!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_03_Gosship_36
string.body: How dare you?!

string.name: STR_IDAb1_Ere_Start_Drakan_High_Fi_74_Ae_Idle_H
string.body: Kill the intruders!

string.name: STR_IDAb1_Ere_Start_Drakan_High_Fi_74_Ae_Die_H
string.body: Damn it!

string.name: STR_IDAb1_Ere_Bridge_Drakan_High_As_74_Ae_Idle_H
string.body: What's going on here?!

string.name: STR_IDAb1_Ere_Bridge_Drakan_High_As_74_Ae_Die_H
string.body: Quick! Deliver the news!

string.name: STR_IDAb1_Ere_Bridge_Drakan_High_Wi_74_Ae_Idle_H
string.body: Did you think I would just let you go?

string.name: STR_IDAb1_Ere_Bridge_Drakan_High_Wi_74_Ae_Die_H
string.body: Curse you, Daevas…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1Round_Gossip_40
string.body: Only a cleric can absorb the essence.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_DG_01
string.body: I hate irritating things with wings…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_DG_02
string.body: Get out of my way!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_DG_03
string.body: We're saved!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_01
string.body: You will be able to open the Purification Jail, if you first get the Unsealing Device.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_02
string.body: Another Daeva was taken to the Chamber of Punishment in my place. I haven't seen him since. Please rescue him.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_03
string.body: The Balaur lock up rebellious Daevas in the Rehabilitation Jail. Using the Pulley, they hoist their new cage up high into the sky.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_04
string.body: It's said some supervisors in the prison camp carry bombs with them.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_05
string.body: It's said some supervisors in the prison camp carry bombs with them.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_06_1
string.body: The 1st floor of the prison has a power generator. Please destroy it and rescue the Daevas.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_06_2
string.body: Thank you for saving me... Thank you...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_06_3
string.body: Up in the Disassembly Room, there's a person looking for someone. I wonder if they managed to find them...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_07
string.body: If you have a key to the Room of Meditation, you can use it to open or close the room at the 3rd floor of the Prison Camp.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_08
string.body: There are even spirits locked up in the Atonement Room. I can't believe they managed to catch spirits...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_09
string.body: You can use the bombs to destroy the facilities within the prison camp.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_VG_01
string.body: I'll take care of things here. Go find the other Daevas!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_VG_02
string.body: My son and the other detachment members are not here. Just… tell me if you find them?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_10
string.body: Daeva, help me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_DG_04
string.body: Intruder! I need to go report….

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_11
string.body: Thank you for rescuing me! The Balaur have keys to release the other Daevas!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_DG_05
string.body: So the fleeing rats have returned on their nest!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_12
string.body: I sneaked after the Daevas and found the exit! AND a Balaur treasure! There are plenty who need it more than I do, though.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_13
string.body: The storage is collapsing!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_14_1
string.body: I will have my revenge...

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_14_2
string.body: I will not leave until I see Kudansha's heart with my own eyes!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_14_3
string.body: Did you kill Kudansha?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_15_1_Li
string.body: Motor… Where are you?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_15_2_Li
string.body: Now that I found my friend, I want out of here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_15_3_Li
string.body: Motor, you're alive!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_15_1_Da
string.body: Bigachen… Where are you?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_15_2_Da
string.body: Now that I found my friend, I want out of here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_15_3_Da
string.body: Bigachen, you're okay!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_16_1
string.body: Ugh…. Ow….

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_16_2
string.body: I don't think… I'll be okay…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_16_3
string.body: Did you get the Secret Remedy of Revival?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_17_1
string.body: Help me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_17_2
string.body: Please, keep me safe until I find my friend!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_18
string.body: Thank you, Daeva!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_19
string.body: I won't forget this!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_20
string.body: I am indebted to you…

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTM_Lobby_21
string.body: The match time is 8 minutes. But beware: unlike individual matches, there is no overtime for group battles.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTM_Lobby_22
string.body: The match time is 8 minutes but after 6 minutes, fever time starts. Fever time means that the ground starts to burn and you can take damage from Dancing Fire, nyerk nyerk.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTM_Lobby_23
string.body: You win if you manage to wipe out the opposing team. If there are still team members standing when the time is up, the team who killed the most opponents wins!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDInfinity_Gosship_01
string.body: All right! Show me what you can do.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDInfinity_Gosship_02
string.body: Amazing. I've been waiting for a Daeva like you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDInfinity_Gosship_03
string.body: This is your chance to make your name known to the Empyrean Lord.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDInfinity_Gosship_04
string.body: Someone like you should have no problems with the next floor either.

string.name: STR_WORLD_CHAT_PADET_KOBONG_GOSSHIP_01
string.body: There are too many living things in Atreia, way more than necessary, guh!

string.name: STR_WORLD_CHAT_PADET_KOBONG_GOSSHIP_02
string.body: What's the point of churning out new weapons when you lack insight, guh?

string.name: STR_WORLD_CHAT_PADET_KOBONG_GOSSHIP_03
string.body: Don't babble when you don't know half of it, guh!

string.name: STR_WORLD_CHAT_PADET_DRYARARE_GOSSHIP_01
string.body: Crusher will be seed of new era, nyerk!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Witch_01
string.body: Ah, uninvited guests....

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Witch_02
string.body: Not bad, for peons.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Witch_03
string.body: Did you think I would simply let you pass?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Witch_04
string.body: Hah, you DO have some bite to you....

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Witch_05
string.body: Well, I suppose I needn't pull my punches, then.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Witch_06
string.body: You fools!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Witch_07
string.body: Your tenacity is commendable, but this ends NOW.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Witch_08
string.body: This is not over!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Boss_01
string.body: Ugh, you aren't even a challenge.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Boss_02
string.body: You puny ants!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Boss_03
string.body: For the queen!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Boss_04
string.body: Hah, all right. NOW this is fun....

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Boss_05
string.body: Do not mistake me for some grunt....

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Boss_06
string.body: Ereshkigal grant me strength!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Boss_07
string.body: NO! That shield was blessed by Ereshkigal herself.... It was unbreakable!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Boss_08
string.body: Hah! Behold, the perfect defense!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Boss_09
string.body: I will eradicate every one of you cursed insects!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Boss_10
string.body: You will know true terror....

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAbRe_Core_03_Boss_01
string.body: Sing me a dirge....

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAbRe_Core_03_Boss_02
string.body: My life for Ereshkigal!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAbRe_Core_03_Boss_03
string.body: I cannot be silenced.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAbRe_Core_03_Boss_04
string.body: Sing, frozen souls!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAbRe_Core_03_Boss_05
string.body: Your very spirit will freeze....

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAbRe_Core_03_move_01
string.body: I will break you.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_BossEnd_01
string.body: We'll take it from here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAbRe_Core_03_Doll_Monster_01
string.body: Intruders!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAbRe_Core_03_Doll_Monster_02
string.body: Where did they go?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAbRe_Core_03_Doll_Monster_03
string.body: Hey, get away from there!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAbRe_Core_03_Doll_Monster_04
string.body: The legion shall rise again!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Ab1_SiM_BroadCaster_L_01
string.body: The Elyos are preparing siege cannons in an Upper Layer fortress.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Ab1_SiM_BroadCaster_L_02
string.body: The Elyos are preparing siege cannons in 2 Upper Layer fortresses.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Ab1_SiM_BroadCaster_L_03
string.body: The Elyos are preparing siege cannons in 3 Upper Layer fortresses.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Ab1_SiM_BroadCaster_D_01
string.body: The Asmodians are preparing siege cannons in an Upper Layer fortress.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Ab1_SiM_BroadCaster_D_02
string.body: The Asmodians are preparing siege cannons in 2 Upper Layer fortresses.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Ab1_SiM_BroadCaster_D_03
string.body: The Asmodians are preparing siege cannons in 3 Upper Layer fortresses.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_Avatar_TreasureBox_01
string.body: I need Illusion Marks to open the box.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Gosship_01
string.body: Let me know when you're ready to go!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Gosship_02
string.body: We've got to destroy this place. It's the only way out!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Gosship_03
string.body: Hurry! Before the whole thing collapses!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Gosship_04
string.body: Over here--let's get moving!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Gosship_05
string.body: We've been ordered to retreat.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Heroes_Gosship_06
string.body: Please tell me if you wish to return to Lakrum.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Event_Moon_Gosship_01
string.body: Please don't hit me!

string.name: STR_CHAT_Event_Moon_Gosship_02
string.body: Ouch! It hurts!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDEternity_02_Guard_Gosship_01
string.body: This is a dead end. Find another way.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_2_F2P_Goship_01
string.body: We'll take care of things here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_2_F2P_Goship_02
string.body: We'll take care of things here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_2_F2P_Goship_03
string.body: We'll take care of things here.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTiamat_2_F2P_Goship_04
string.body: This is under control. Onward, to Tiamat!

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1_Quest_Goossip_01
string.body: [%username]! Over here! Look at this!

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1_Quest_Goossip_02
string.body: Odella... is... being crystallized!

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF1_Quest_Goossip_03
string.body: Where are they moving the Odella?

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF3_Quest_Goossip_01
string.body: Here's the Daeva that the Hoarfrost Chieftan talked about!

string.name: STR_CHAT_DF3_Quest_Goossip_02
string.body: It's written in Balaur. I can't read it.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTemple_Low_Quest_Goossip_01
string.body: You obtained the confidential document from Agile Malika Churaga!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDTemple_Low_Quest_Goossip_02

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_IDF7_Mine_Prison_Undead_67_An_3_2

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_01
string.body: The Balaur Lord's Chest that the Stellin employees are moving has been spotted. Word is, they're using the sewage drain.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_02
string.body: The ST-IX Chest has been discovered at the Research Center! The contents are the same as the Balaur Lord's Chest that was found at the entrance. It seems that the Balaur Lord's Legacy is used for the creation of ST-IX.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_03
string.body: The ST-IX Extraction Tube has been discovered! The power extracted from the Balaur Lord is separated into pure power and then the remaining residue before being moved. Where are they sending it?

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_04
string.body: The Test Tube with the Balaur Subject has been discovered! What a strange device, full of mystery. What are they doing with it?

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_05
string.body: What is this? This surge... of power! Aaah!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_06
string.body: You saved me... me, who was abandoned by my kin.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_07
string.body: Pathetic! Defeated by a filthy mutant! Move aside, I'll handle this!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_08
string.body: Ugh... I shall become even stronger!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_09
string.body: How did you find me? Die!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_10
string.body: This is just the beginning for the Regatus... Vishaka... I wish you great success.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_11
string.body: How dare you! Be gone!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_12
string.body: You won't be granted a peaceful death!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_13
string.body: Whoever defeats that intruder shall be rewarded!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_14
string.body: How dare you bring that mutant!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_15
string.body: A Daeva bastard and a disgrace to the Balaur? What a pair!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_16
string.body: I know your kind, traveling with cursed blood... hahaha!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_17
string.body: We were only born differently... why are all Balaur so....

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_18
string.body: Cruel Balaur... this is unforgivable.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_19
string.body: I'm not a disgrace! I'll prove it!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_20
string.body: Unknown intruder detected! Entry not permitted! Entry not permitted!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_21
string.body: You dirty Stellin bastards, keep your promises!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_22
string.body: I won't forgive those that are after Apsu's legacy!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_23
string.body: Stop spreading ST-IX! You are poisoning my people!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_24
string.body: Be gone with you, Stellin bastards!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_25
string.body: Stellin... I will rip off your dirty masks....

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_26
string.body: One... two... I forgot how many. This won't be forgiven.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_27
string.body: Those who interfere... with our task... will be killed.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_28
string.body: Must meet the quota... go away.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_29
string.body: The Regatus Headquarters was wiped out, but Vishaka got away. I also encountered a strange girl. This needs to be reported to the Leader.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Mission_30
string.body: I won't steal anymore and live the straight and narrow.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Donas_Gossip_01
string.body: Time is going by so slow! Oh, wait, I just got to work....

string.name: STR_CHAT_Donas_Gossip_02
string.body: Hmm, why can't everyone just work without being forced?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Donas_Gossip_03
string.body: Hmph! I need to go, I have some urgent business to take care of....

string.name: STR_CHAT_Donas_Gossip_04
string.body: When you're a leader, you never get to rest.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Monan_Gossip_01
string.body: How's everyone been doing?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Monan_Gossip_02
string.body: Existential dread and fear for my future ensures that I lie awake at night, too exhausted to sleep.

string.name: STR_CHAT_Monan_Gossip_03
string.body: A promotion will mean I'm further shackled to this company, but what else do I have in my life?

string.name: STR_CHAT_Monan_Gossip_04

string.body: Top of the morning! You look like you could use some training!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F4_IDAb1_MiniCastle
string.body: Top of the morning! You know, if you trained more, you could finally turn into an honorable Daeva!

string.name: STR_CHAT_F5_IDAb1_MiniCastle
string.body: Top of the morning! Your discharge date is coming up! Give me five pushups!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_MiniCastle_01
string.body: We will take care of those below. Go up there, capture the artifact, and push! Remember--the Drakes, Keepers, Castle Gates, and the Guardian General are the important targets.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_MiniCastle_02
string.body: Use a siege weapon to destroy the castle gate, and then advance and defeat the Guardian General.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_Ere_1R_G_15_1_BOTH
string.body: I heard my friend's screams in there! Hurry, we need to find him!

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_MiniCastle_03
string.body: That's all for training! Practice hard until next time!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Stellium_01
string.body: Good news for all Daevas with Stellium! If you have Stellium, I will exchange it for rewards!

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Stellium_02
string.body: You can use the Stellium coins to purchase various rewards or you can use them directly.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Aside_01
string.body: The Leader is not here right now. If you need to talk to him, come back between 9AM and 6PM.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Aside_02
string.body: I wish I could ditch work too. Oh, I'm sorry! I didn't mean to say that out loud.

string.name: STR_GOSSHIP_LDF8_Aside_03
string.body: I wonder why the Leader isn't getting fired?

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_MiniCastle_04
string.body: The artifact is up there! However, I would recommend you take them all out if you want to level up quickly.

string.name: STR_CHAT_IDAb1_MiniCastle_05

string.body: Time to turn up the heat!
